criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adults aged 65 years old or over;

          -  Hip fracture with X-ray-confirmed femoral neck, trochanteric or sub-trochanteric
             fracture;

          -  Within 21 days of a hip fracture;

          -  Willingness to sign informed consent form;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with pathological fractures;

          -  With terminal malignancies.
